node.text:
This was the last stop in our journey and final episode. We got to check out how the @toyotaUSA RAV4 Hybrid is built and then put it to the test. We had lots of fun pit stops along the way with farms, horses, and wrapped it all up with an epic climbing session in the gorge. This is what it's all about. Everything in between makes the journey an adventure. Onward to the next one. #LetsGoPlaces

🎥 @tczech 
⌨️ @rodophoto 
🧗🏽‍♀️ @maya__fields

🎥 @tczech 
⌨️ @rodophoto 
🎣 @brockfuller

node.text:
At the end of the day, the process is the journey for me. It's the adventure in itself. I got a chance to head back to my home state of Texas to see how @ToyotaUSA builds each Tundra from start to finish. Right in the heart of San Antonio is where we started, and then hit the road to test out the new Tundra TRD as we made our way to Big Bend National Park. What a time we had. Hope you guys enjoy! #Tundra #LetsGoPlaces 

🎥 @tczech
Editor: @rodophoto 
@inkwell.media

node.text: Alright here is the update for everyone asking about the Basesets Workshop! Appreciate your patience and questions about everything. I wanted to give you more insight on what it’s going to be about, why it was delayed, and when it’s launching. Early May it’ll be here and ready to purchase for you guys. Thanks again and happy to answer anyone’s questions 🙏🏻

node.text: Off we go 🛫 🇮🇸 I mentioned in my stories,  but this trip is about more than just resetting. It’s about stillness and figuring out my passion again. Things move fast in life and sometimes I lose track of who I am, where I’m going, all of it. I put so much pressure on myself to succeed and elevate that I lose track of what’s important. Hope you guys enjoy following along. The vlog from here will be special. 🙏🏻

node.text:
This was the last stop in our journey and final episode. We got to check out how the @toyotaUSA RAV4 Hybrid is built and then put it to the test. We had lots of fun pit stops along the way with farms, horses, and wrapped it all up with an epic climbing session in the gorge. This is what it's all about. Everything in between makes the journey an adventure. Onward to the next one. #LetsGoPlaces

🎥 @tczech 
⌨️ @rodophoto 
🧗🏽‍♀️ @maya__fields

node.text:

node.text:
The In The Field Storytellers Workshop is officially live! Couldn’t be more stoked to have this out there. Each piece of my process was revealed in this workshop, and I feel humbled to be apart of something like this alongside the team involved. It’s been a fun one and I’m excited to hear your thoughts on it. 🙏🏻🖥🎥 Team below //

Cinematographer: @cassheridan 
AC: @dylonelfuego 
Audio Sound Mixer: @jeffpaceaudio 
Model: @taylorsaxelby 
Model: @kiaraasiaa 
Surfer & Slate: @b.taut 
Stunt Rider: @parker.pitman 
Behind the Scenes: @sethvdl

node.text: Here is a look into my In The Field Storytellers Workshop. I bring you into my viewfinder so you can see how I construct my narrative through photography. More info on this in my stories, sign up to receive updates, and last but not least, PRESALE for early bird discount goes live tomorrow morning! 👀👏🏻
